hew |last22=Jernigan |first22=Daniel |last23=Reed |first23=Carrie |title=Community Mitigation Guidelines to Prevent Pandemic Influenza\u2014United States, 2017 |journal=MMWR. Recommendations and Reports |date=21 April 2017 |volume=66 |issue=1 |pages=1\u201334 |doi=10.15585/mmwr.rr6601a1 |pmid=28426646 |pmc=5837128}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NY0JD\">{{cite web |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/what-it-means-to-contain-and-mitigate-the-coronavirus |title=What It Means to Contain and Mitigate the Coronavirus |first=Robert P. |last=Baird |date=11 March 2020 |work=[[The New Yorker]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RwmYm\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/07/world/asia/china-coronavirus-cost.html |title=China May Be Beating the Coronavirus, at a Painful Cost |first=Amy |last=Qin |work=[[The New York Times]] |date=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"shZdf\">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/11/mass-testing-alerts-and-big-fines-the-strategies-used-in-asia-to-slow-coronavirus |title=Mass testing, alerts and big fines: the strategies used in Asia to slow coronavirus |first1=Justin McCurry Rebecca Ratcliffe in |last1=Bangkok |first2=Helen Davidson in Hong |last2=Kong |date=11 March 2020 |work=[[The Guardian]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hxm4a\">{{cite web |url=https://www.ebmedicine.net/topics/infectious-disease/COVID-19 |title=Novel Coronavirus\u2014COVID-19: What Emergency Clinicians Need to Know |work=EBMedicine.net |access-date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"iR2Oj\">{{cite web |url=https://www.schengenvisainfo.com/news/schengen-area-crisis-eu-states-close-borders-as-coronavirus-outbreak-grips-bloc/ |title=Schengen Area Crisis: EU States Close Borders as Coronavirus Outbreak Grips Bloc |website=Schengen Visa Information |date=13 March 2020 |accessdate=16 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IVdfl\">{{cite web |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/coronavirus-updates-5-dead-200-infected-italy-europe-braces-covid-n1141466 |title=Coronavi