ai (\u90ed\u8d85\u51ef) |last2=Li |first2=Yanan (\u674e\u4e9a\u5357) |work=China News Service}}</ref>\n\n}}\n<!--==Sources attribution==-->* {{Free-content attribution |title=290 million students out of school due to COVID-19: UNESCO releases first global numbers and mobilizes response |publisher=UNESCO |documentURL= https://en.unesco.org/news/290-million-students-out-school-due-covid-19-unesco-releases-first-global-numbers-and-mobilizes |licence statement URL= https://en.unesco.org/news/290-million-students-out-school-due-covid-19-unesco-releases-first-global-numbers-and-mobilizes |licence=CC BY-SA 3.0 IGO|howto=no }}\n*{{Free-content attribution |title=Coronavirus impacts education |publisher=UNESCO |documentURL= https://en.unesco.org/themes/education-emergencies/coronavirus-school-closures |licence statement URL= https://en.unesco.org/themes/education-emergencies/coronavirus-school-closures |licence=CC BY-SA 3.0 IGO|howto=no }}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{Sister project links|voy=2019\u20132020 coronavirus pandemic|c=category:COVID-19 pandemic|d=Q81068910|q=no|b=no|v=no|s=Category:COVID-19|m=no|mw=no|wikt=COVID-19|species=Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2|n=Category:COVID-19}}\n{{Scholia}}\n\n===Government health agencies===\n\n* [https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019 COVID-19] ([http://www.who.int/news-room/q-a-detail/q-a-coronaviruses Questions & Answers], [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLbpi6ZahtOH5PLTT1yfXxcxDsNM40N1uG Instructional Videos]) by the [[World Health Organization]]\n* [https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/novel-coronavirus-china COVID-19] ([http://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/novel-coronavirus-china/questions-answers Q&A]) by the [[European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control]]\n* [http://en.nhc.gov.cn/antivirusfight.html COVID-19] by the [[China National Health Commission]]\n* [https://www.moh.gov.sg/covid-19 COVID-19] ([http://www.moh.gov.sg/covid-19/faqs Q&A]) by the [[Singapore Ministry of Health]]\n* [h